# Install

* Prerequisite: Ubuntu 16.04
* son-cli
* son-examples
* apt install sshpass
* Configure Docker Engine API to listen on TCP port:
```$ systemctl edit docker
[Service]
ExecStart=
ExecStart=/usr/bin/dockerd -H fd:// -H tcp://127.0.0.1:2376```
* Install Agents
```bash misc/vim-emu/agents/build.sh```
